reviewText:
I bought this dvd last year but due to life circumstance have not made the time to open it until now. Unfortunately the dvd case was empty. It is obviously too late to return it.

Obviously i cant write a real review of the dvd, sorry.

Amazons return policy is pretty good so if yours arrives empty you can always refer to my review as a precedent.

Good luck !
excellent source on the art.  shows master students and teachers just going crazy.  make sure to purchase the beginner series first.
